# Components List — Smart Medication Adherence Verification System

| Component | Quantity | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ESP32 Dev Board | 1 | Main microcontroller, Wi-Fi + MQTT |
| IR Sensor Module | 3 | One per medicine compartment, digital output |
| Status LED | 3 | One per compartment, indicates active alert |
| MicroSD Card Module | 1 | SPI interface, stores recorded audio (WAV) |
| OLED Display (128x64) | 1 | I2C interface, status/feedback display |
| INMP441 Microphone Module | 1 | I2S digital mic, voice confirmation |
| Breadboard | 1 | Full-size, for prototyping wiring |
| Jumper Wires | Multiple | Various lengths, module interconnects |
